Background

		Mr. Miguel Vizcarrondo has been Executive Vice President of Payment Services at EVERTEC, Inc. since and EVERTEC Group, LLC since April 17, 2012 and served as its Head of the ATH Network, Merchant Acquiring Business, Business Development & Sales since April 17, 2012 until May 9, 2017. Mr. Vizcarrondo served as Executive Vice President, Head of Merchant Acquiring Business and Ath Network at EVERTEC, Inc. and EVERTEC Group, LLC since February 22, 2012. Prior to that, he ... served as Senior Vice President and Head of the Merchant Acquiring Business of EVERTEC, Inc. and EVERTEC Group, LLC. He joined EVERTEC, Inc. in 2010 as a Senior Vice President and Head of Merchant Acquiring. Prior to that, he served for Banco Popular since 2006. From 2000 to 2006, he served as Vice President of Corporate Banking at Banco Popular. From 1996 to 2000, Mr. Vizcarrondo served as Portfolio Manager–Treasury Division for Banco Popular. Mr. Vizcarrondo received his Bachelor of Science in Management, with a concentration in Finance, from Tulane University in New Orleans, Louisiana.Read Full Background




