Miguel Vizcarrondo



Mr. Miguel Vizcarrondo is Executive VP & Head-Merchant Acquiring Business at EVERTEC, Inc. and Executive VP & Head-Merchant Acquiring Business at EVERTEC Group LLC. He is on the Board of Directors at Pee Wee Football League of Puerto Rico and Association for Financial Professionals Puerto Rico, Inc.
Mr. Vizcarrondo was previously employed as Senior VP & Head-Merchant Acquiring Business by Banco Popular de Puerto Rico.
He received his undergraduate degree from Tulane University (Louisiana).



